node.text:
I’m proud to launch a 100% pure cashmere Home Collection with @NakedCashmere today! NAKEDCASHMERE has been a favorite of mine for years, when designing this collection I wanted to invoke that same feeling of coziness, yet chicness; with lots of layers and textures. This sustainable 18-piece collection brings the ultimate level of luxury into your everyday life.
#nakedhomewithashleystark 
📸 @brittanyambridge
